     6	/**
     7	 * The Tevm EVM is in charge of executing bytecode. It is a very light wrapper around ethereumjs EVM
     8	 * The Evm class provides tevm specific typing with regard to the custom stateManager. It does not
     9	 * provide custom typing to the blockchain or common objects.
    10	 * @example
    11	 * ```typescript
